trans-unit.source: Represents a hash set that mutates with little or no memory allocations and that can produce or build on immutable hash set instances very efficiently.
trans-unit.target: Representa un conjunto de hash que transforma con poca o ninguna asignación de memoria y que puede generar o compilar instancias de conjunto hash inmutables muy eficazmente.

trans-unit.source: **NuGet package**: <see href="https://www.nuget.org/packages/System.Collections.Immutable/">System.Collections.Immutable</see> (<see href="https://docs.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.collections.immutable?#Remarks">about immutable collections and how to install</see>)
trans-unit.target: **Paquete NuGet**: <see href="https://www.nuget.org/packages/System.Collections.Immutable/">System.Collections.Immutable</see> (<see href="https://docs.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.collections.immutable?#Remarks">sobre las colecciones inmutables y la instalación</see>)

trans-unit.source: Although <xref:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableHashSet%601.Union%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> and other methods already provide fast bulk change operations on a collection, the <xref:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableHashSet%601.Builder> class allows multiple combinations of changes to be made to a set with equal efficiency.
trans-unit.target: Aunque <xref:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableHashSet%601.Union%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> y otros métodos ya proporcionan las operaciones de cambio rápido de forma masiva en una colección, el <xref:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableHashSet%601.Builder> clase permite varias combinaciones de los cambios que se realizan en un conjunto con eficacia igual.
